Mobile-first, fully responsive design. remember to use the mobile-first approach. 

favicon link source https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EIRSVi/eirsvi/refs/heads/docs/assets/image/288bc158-5999-425d-846e-4c0824f2294e.png 

Technology stack: strictly HTML, CSS, and JavaScript only. 
Prepare a professional, future-proof folder and file directory structure. such as components, pages, assets, styles, scripts, and static and more  for the future project.
 


Project Structure & Layouts:
- no color for header and footer style and make sure it fit screen size and responsive. their is not toolbar for navigation scroll down and up left and right.
- Centered, sticky icon navigation bar (Home | Article | Resource | Matrix | Sort)
A navbar that changes width on active page. 
Icons:
- Use Font Awesome icon font.
- all icons must be dark or black color.  
- Icons must be responsive and animated.
- icon hover must be emerald color.

  - Icons:
    - Home: <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
    - Article: <i class="fa-solid fa-feather"></i>
    - Resource: <i class="fa-solid fa-passport"></i>
    - Matrix: <i class="fa-solid fa-shapes"></i>
    - Sort: <i class="fa-solid fa-signature"></i>
Navigation: 
- All navigation between menu/navbar links must be client-side (no page refresh).
- make sure mobile device responsive design
- show the menu navbar  on mobile devices or pc theme the same  as desktop theme layout.
-  make sure the menu navbar  is always visible. and don't show navbar title text below the icon. 
